	(text "Schottky Datasheet:\n@ 25°C and 300mA avg current draw ~= 250mV forward voltage\n\nBuck needs to output 5.25V:\n-> Using R_{FBT} = (V_{OUT} - V_{REF})/V_{REF} * R_{FBB}\n-> R_{FBT} = (5.25V - 1V)=/1V * (11kOhm) = 46.75kOhm (~47kOhm)"
		(exclude_from_sim no)
		(at 58.928 24.638 0)
		(effects
